# ─── DATABASE (PostgreSQL) ───────────────────────────────────────
# For LOCAL DEV: create a free database at https://neon.tech
# Copy the connection string from the Neon dashboard.
#
# DATABASE_URL = pooled connection (used at runtime by the app)
# DIRECT_URL   = direct connection (used by Prisma for migrations/push)
#
# Neon provides both in the dashboard — paste them below:
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@ep-xxx-pooler.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require"
DIRECT_URL="postgresql://user:password@ep-xxx.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require"
